Text: Re V VErrol NRON PM To Andrea R CT cc Subject Re V V Andrea These deals have been changed to NYMEX swaps Thanks Errol X From Andrea R Guillen ECT PM Sent by Andrea R CT To Errol NRON Laura NRON cc Larry Joe CT Subject V V Hi I received a call from BNP Paribas on these two EOL deals The trader at BNP talked to Dutch about changing the deals from Gas Daily to Nymex please let me know Thanks Angie

Re QF EOL QF EOL look at QF per BNP Paribas this deal should be fixed price we show Thank you Angie Forwarded by Andrea R GuillenHOUECT on AM From Diane Anderson ENRON AM To Andrea R CT cc Subject Re QF EOL QF EOL this is for the two Paribas deals that Carmens been looking for please confirm that theyve been fixed so we can sign Forwarded by Diane AndersonNAEnron on AM Errol McLaughlin PM To Diane nron cc Subject Re QF EOL QF EOL This deal has been changed to a NYMEX swap at Thanks Errol Enron North America Corp From Diane Anderson AM To Errol NRON cc Subject QF EOL QF EOL Hi Errol Have you had any luck with these two deals Thanks Diane Forwarded by Diane AndersonNAEnron on AM Enron North America Corp From Diane Anderson AM To Errol NRON Sherry nron cc Subject QF EOL QF EOL Hi Errol Sherry We received confirmations for the above referenced deals from Paribas they confirm us and Paribas confirm differs from what we show in TAGG Paribas trader Herve says that he spoke with John Arnold after the deal was done and changed the price from to and the index from Gas Daily to NYMEX TAGG still reflects the terms that EOL has Can one of you please find out if John Arnold agreed to these changes and if so can you make the necessary changes to TAGG Let me know Thanks a lot Diane
